{
  "stem": "25639.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we had to sort of keep a low profile that she-- that she's my mother, and Anushka is my sister.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were-- we had a Hungarian guard, who sometimes spoke Hungarian to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was a blessing, because once in a while he-- he would tell us that he came from Hungary and that he has a grandchild.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he would take his wallet out and show his grandchild to us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he sort of held it out like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- but he couldn't talk just any time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This really was very rare, but once in a while he did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And Anushka would take some soap, if she found soap-- a bar of soap-- she would take it and put it in his pocket.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he didn't say yes, he didn't say no, he didn't say thank you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He just stood there and just sort of smiled a little.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And mother encouraged Anushka to do this when she finds something that was hard to get during war time, and that he-- something that he would appreciate, and something small.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so there were other things that she put into his pocket.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And now this guard turned out to be very helpful later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I want to just tell you a few incidents that happened in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As you know, each area was surrounded by tall electric wire fences, at least twice as tall as an average human being.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Near the Kanada work detail, the very next area, surrounded by electric wire fences, of course, was the twin lager.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there were twins with bandages on, and all sorts of-- with all sorts of problems.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
